# Comment Rules
- All code comments must be written in English
- Comments should be clear, concise, and descriptive
- Use proper English grammar and punctuation
- Avoid slang or informal language in comments
- Include comments for complex logic or important business rules
- Document function parameters and return values in English
- Keep comments up to date with code changes
